Eddie C. RISDAL, Appellant, v. Terry MAPES, Warden; Paul Fitzgerald, Story County Sheriff, Appellees. No. 06-1410. United States Court of Appeals, Eighth Circuit. Submitted: Dec. 29, 2006. Filed: Jan. 10, 2007. Eddie C. Risdal, Cherokee, IA, pro se. Before SMITH, MAGILL, and BENTON, Circuit Judges.

[UNPUBLISHED]

PER CURIAM.

Eddie Risdal appeals the judgment of the district court1 dismissing his 42 U.S.C. § 1983 complaint prior to service. Following careful review of the record and Ris*551dal’s arguments on appeal, we affirm the judgment of the district court. See 8th Cir. R. 47B.

. The Honorable James E. Gritzner, United States District Judge for the Southern District of Iowa.
